race.description: Thank You To All Our Sponsors Mdn
race.comment: STORM AWAY (7) was strong first-up at Ascot before tackling the Belgravia Stakes last start over 1200m. Up slightly in trip today, but he drops right back to a maiden. He's shown he's much stronger than this grade and can pick up his maiden victory in this suitable assignment. RISING FAME (8) was only fair first-up but bounced right back to form last start when leading the field off a short freshen, beaten 2L. The wide draw is a query, but she does have early speed to offset the alley. Improvement is expected now and she's sure to be right in the finish. FINAL CALL (2) showed he's ready to fire first-up in a recent heat at Lark Hill where he got the job done. This trip first-up looks perfect and he should land in a great spot in running. He makes plenty of appeal. ITZABEAST (1) is third-up now and can raise the bar. VIRESHA (12) will be better for the debut performance and is not to be discounted.
